410
00:21:08,067 --> 00:21:11,368
ikh freg aykh, ven di sovyetishe VLAST' iz gekumen,

411
00:21:11,863 --> 00:21:13,738
di daytshn zenen avek,

412
00:21:14,361 --> 00:21:19,336
m'hot gekhapt epes fun di politsistn, fun di Ukrayner, fun di Rumener?

413
00:21:19,336 --> 00:21:22,607
