414
00:21:21,944 --> 00:21:25,243
m'hot zey, a bisl arestirt, a bisl UNK.

415
00:21:22,900 --> 00:21:24,412
m'hot zey gesudyet?

416
00:21:25,243 --> 00:21:28,486
s'iz geven eyner a pol-, a krist...

417
00:21:29,317 --> 00:21:31,233
mayn man iz geven a blekher.

418
00:21:31,233 --> 00:21:36,803
fleg ile yor kumen ⟨a⟩ UNK krist,

419
00:21:37,041 --> 00:21:40,663
