420
00:21:41,040 --> 00:21:43,872
zenen mir geven zeyer gut mit zey.

421
00:21:43,872 --> 00:21:51,446
der shver fleg zey ⟨ley⟩tn varenyes, honik, ibergezotene puter, azoyne zakhn, keyn Ades.

422
00:21:51,553 --> 00:21:53,673
iz men gekumen tsu forn.

423
00:21:54,591 --> 00:22:00,963
zey hobn gekoyft a shtub un z-... un der man iz geven a PREDATEL'. er hot,

424
00:22:00,582 --> 00:22:01,993
der profesor?

425
00:22:01,425 --> 00:22:05,387
er ho- er hot, er hot, gefirt di role.

426
00:22:05,387 --> 00:22:09,147
⟨⟩, flegn zey geyn ile zuntik,

427
00:22:09,171 --> 00:22:12,614
 fr- shabes oyf der nakht, in kloyster arayn,

428
00:22:12,614 --> 00:22:14,298
un zogn UNK,

429
00:22:14,298 --> 00:22:22,057
m'vet boven fun kinder, ⟨⟩, zoln mir boven, vent; fun, eltere mentshn zoln mir leygn stelyes.

430
00:22:22,333 --> 00:22:25,666
iz men gezesn un m'hot geredt.

431
00:22:25,666 --> 00:22:27,457
flegn zey tomed geyn.

432
00:22:27,868 --> 00:22:35,138
