433
00:22:35,138 --> 00:22:36,961
az m'hot undz aroysgeshikt,

434
00:22:36,961 --> 00:22:39,759
nu, zenen mir geven azoy NESCHASTNe.

435
00:22:40,137 --> 00:22:42,763
az mir zenen gekumen tsu forn,

436
00:22:43,090 --> 00:22:46,391
⟨i-, f-, a-,⟩ tomed,

437
00:22:46,549 --> 00:22:50,105
ikh fleg, zeyer gut kokhn, bakn.

438
00:22:50,105 --> 00:22:56,702
fleg er kumen d-, UNK shikn politsayen, az me zol mikh nemen POD VINTOVKe tsun im.

439
00:22:56,792 --> 00:23:03,148
kumen tsu geyn, iz vos ⟨zi⟩ hot mir gezogt, dos hob ikh geton. ikh bin geven tsu zey farkoyft.

440
00:23:02,074 --> 00:23:03,063
yo.

441
00:23:03,441 --> 00:23:06,052
az ikh bin geven tsu zey farkoyft,

442
00:23:06,141 --> 00:23:10,877
zenen mir, fleg er mikh opfirn un fleg mikh brengen.

443
00:23:10,877 --> 00:23:12,845
ikh hob gelozt di kinder.

444
00:23:12,845 --> 00:23:16,947
mayn shviger iz gezesn funem nayntsetn yor

445
00:23:16,947 --> 00:23:24,017
bizkele GITLER iz arayn. ven GITLER ⟨z-,⟩ kumt nit, efsher volt zi nokh geven gelebt. a gezunte yidene a sheyne,

446
00:23:24,017 --> 00:23:26,722
