496
00:26:43,390 --> 00:26:47,403
nu, m'hot zey azoy lang gehaltn un m'hot zey oykh aroysgeshikt.

497
00:26:47,403 --> 00:26:49,938
vuhin m'hot zey aroysgeshikt, veys ikh nit,

498
00:26:49,938 --> 00:26:53,226
